U.K. Stocks Decline, Reversing Earlier Advance in Benchmark FTSE 100 Index

-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 
2011-09-01T07:11:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-01/u-k-stocks-decline-reversing-earlier-advance-in-benchmark-ftse-100-index.html
U.K. stocks declined, with the
benchmark FTSE 100 Index dropping 8.28, or 0.2 percent, to
5,386.25 as of 8:11 a.m. in  London . The gauge had earlier
climbed as much as 0.4 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
